Kuthiwa imoto iphume emgwaqweni u-Otto Bluff yashayisa abantu ababili abebehamba ngezinyawo. UMnuz Russel Meiring, okhulumela abezimo eziphuthumayo, u-ER24 uthe ngesikhathi abezimo eziphuthumayo befika endaweni yesehlo bafice ingane eneminyaka emine nonina beseceleni komgwaqo. Bahlole unina nengane bathola ukuthi abalimele kakhulu. Abebesemotweni nabo abalimalanga kakhulu. Bonke abebetubekile balashwe endaweni yesehlo base bedluliselwa esibhedlela.